#

Creamy Pumpkin Soup

40 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodFall Recipe

Description

A smooth and hearty pumpkin soup, perfect for fall, with a hint of sweetness and warmth from spices.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin puree: 2 cups
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • coconut milk: 1 can
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • carrot: 1, diced
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
